Project Report :- Digital literacy
This project report outlines the creation of a Canva-designed infographic aimed at educating students on essential digital literacy topics, including online safety, professional presence, and email etiquette. To make the information accessible, the creator utilized a clean, minimalistic design with clear headings and simple icons, effectively balancing the challenge of being both comprehensive and easy to read. Ultimately, the project served as a valuable exercise that enhanced both the creator's practical design skills and their overall understanding of digital literacy concepts.
